== Executables (Scripts) vs Modules

* Perl
  * Scripts are files with no extension and are executable
  * Or they end with .pl
  * Modules are files with .pm extension
  * They are looked up by the values in @INC
  * They loaded with `use` or `require`

* Perl
  * Scripts are files with no extension and are executable
  * Or they end with .pl
  * Modules are files with .pm extension
  * They are looked up by the values in @INC
